gomodel:5c4605cc00002514
        a                 owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "this paper has mutant phenotype evidence for 4 BP terms\n- bone mineralization involved in bone maturation\t(GO:0035630)\n- tooth eruption (GO:0044691)\n- odontogenesis of dentin-containing tooth (GO:0042475)\n- bone resorption (GO:0045453)" , "it also shows that an osteoclast autonomous function is required for bone resorption and also rescues root formation of molar teeth (i.e. odontogenesis of dentin-containing tooth) as well as tooth eruption of incisors" , "Why does Annotation Preview show a term for 'cellular homeostasis'?" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7476-6306" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5501-853X" ;
        dc:date           "2025-11-19" ;
        dc:title          "Ccdc154 Mus - PMID:20121924 - KRC" ;
        pav:providedBy    "http://informatics.jax.org" ;
        oboInOwl:id       "gomodel:5c4605cc00002514" ;
